      "author": "adanielnoel",
      "description": "This release is a major overhaul of the indexing system. While we previously reindexed the whole vault periodically every few seconds, now we trigger updates immediately on relevant events, and otherwise stay idle.\r\n\r\nBug fixes:\r\n- Some race conditions with Obsidian's file API that were causing updates to fail.\r\n- Titles showing even if the \"Show title property in index\" setting is off.",
